Let \mathbb {H}[x] be the free Heyting algebra with one generator, usually called the Rieger-Nishmura algebra, as shown on the left below. The spectrum \operatorname {Spec}\mathbb {H}[x] as a topological space is the Rieger-Nishimura laddar shown to the right,
